CODE:
class Sequence
{
    // N: input element 
    public static int theSequence(int N)
    {
        // your code here
        // when n=2
        // s(2) = 2 +2*(S(1))=2+2(1+1*1) = 6
        
        if(N == 0){
           return 1;
        }
        
        return N + N * theSequence(N-1);
    }

}

Input:
n = 2
Output: 6
